vectorbeta-desc: Typography refresh of the Vector skin using BetaFeatures
vector-beta-feature-typography-descripti: Updates typography of the Vector skin to improve readability, accessibility and consistency.
vector-beta-feature-compact-personal-bar: Collapses personal bar into a flyout menu.
vector-beta-feature-fixedheader-descript: Turns the header on the default Vector skin into a fixed header.
